title: PROJECT: Fuel Xpress Palmerston
shortDescription: Fuel Xpress Palmerston is a brand-new gas station in Palmerston, Northern Territory. Northern Trade Solutions NT (NTS) were engaged by Sitzler for the design, manufacture and installation of feature cladding, aluminium windows and doors, as well as ceiling and linings of the project.
